@startuml
title Journal Draft Generation — Sequence Diagram

actor Clinician
participant "UI" as UI
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Service" as Service
participant "JournalRenderer" as JR

Clinician -> UI : request generate draft
UI -> Client : generateJournalDraft(caseId)
Client -> Service : generateJournalDraft
Service -> Service : fetch case, patient, latest responses
Service -> JR : renderTemplate(context)
JR --> Service : renderedContent
Service -> Service : save JournalDraft + audit event
Service --> Client : JournalDraft

note right of JR: src/api/journalRenderer.ts

@enduml
